Cation is a minimal TODO app written in Python.

Run on the commandline:

    python3 cation.py <command> <arguments>

Run interactively:

    python3 cation.py

Commands:

    q                                     # Exit
    a <text>                              # Add an item
    d <id>                                # Mark an item as done
    t <id>                                # Mark an item as todo
    o <id>                                # Mark an item as outdated
    x <id>                                # Delete an item
    m <id> <text>                         # Modify the text of an item
    p <id1> <id2>                         # Set <id1> as the parent of <id2>
    l <id1> <id2>                         # Set <id1> as a prerequisite for <id2> (toposort feature pending)
    b <id1> <id2>                         # Break the link between <id1> and <id2>

